        {
            "title": "美元有望在第二季度受益於供應鏈碎片化",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/j0wSDUJwtM7heMCiUgSThw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEAA20GT_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 麥格理銀行表示,隨著美國與伊朗之間的衝突(這也是一場經濟戰爭)重塑全球供應鏈並暴露能源依賴型經濟體的脆弱性,美元可能在第二季度出現反彈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Thierry Wizman在一份報告中指出,從動能戰爭轉向經濟戰爭的轉變,其特徵是美國對霍爾木茲海峽持續封鎖,這創造了有利於美元的條件。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構表示:「如果經濟戰爭在整個第二季度持續,那麼關鍵礦產供應中斷的風險以及對全球經濟供應鏈和經濟體的『非線性』影響應會再次支撐美元。」該機構指出,美國的淨能源平衡為正值,且其經濟具有多元化特性,這些都是抵禦供應衝擊的緩衝。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5e1a663f-126f-3250-b28e-accdb05dfac8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據稱,亞洲面臨的壓力尤其嚴重。麥格理估計,亞洲從中東進口的原油已較戰前水平下降約60%,亞洲原油進口總量下降約30%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">到目前為止,庫存緩衝減輕了這一衝擊,日本和韓國在戰爭爆發時分別持有約224天和200天的淨進口覆蓋量。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但麥格理指出,澳洲僅有33天的覆蓋量,而印度的地下戰略儲備僅約9天,這些國家特別容易受到影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構警告稱,美元走強是衝突持續的條件。麥格理表示,只有在經濟戰爭結束並恢復「關鍵商品的安全通行保障」之後,2025年時代遠離美元的多元化交易才能重新確立。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E5%9C%A8%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%AD%A3%E5%BA%A6%E5%8F%97%E7%9B%8A%E6%96%BC%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E9%8F%88%E7%A2%8E%E7%89%87%E5%8C%96-174244484.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 02:23:11",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "鋰市場低迷期尚未結束?",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/G8dZmiQCfmpJR51avErBug--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED760SU_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 根據Rothschild &amp; Co Redburn的分析,鋰價格面臨新的阻力,該機構警告稱,2027年市場將重返供應過剩局面,這將對價格構成壓力,並削弱主要生產商的投資價值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Mazahir Mammadli更新的供需模型指出三大壓力因素正在匯聚,包括電池產能過剩的逆轉、電動車銷售增長放緩,以及電池容量擴張受限,因為價格實惠的小容量車型銷量超過大型車款。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7e1e0b2d-1c7d-327b-a66b-f87f0859ab25-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">看空論點的核心是中國正在上演的一個動態變化,即電池及電池組件的出口退稅政策將從2027年開始逐步取消。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Rothschild &amp; Co Redburn表示,該行業正以2026年提高產量作為應對措施,提前拉動鋰需求,但該機構認為\"明年這種產能過剩的逆轉將導致鋰需求減速\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在電動車方面,該機構認為中國第一季度銷售疲軟以及北美市場低迷將拖累2026年全球電動車銷售增長至14%,儘管歐洲和發展中市場保持增長勢頭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著中國、阿根廷和美國的供應量不斷增加,Rothschild &amp; Co Redburn預計碳酸鋰當量價格將在\"年底前跌至15-16美元/公斤\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在此背景下,該機構已將雅保(<span><span>Albemarle</span></span>)評級從買入下調至中性,目標價設定為每股188美元,意味著約5%的下行空間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">SQM維持中性評級,修訂目標價為每股83美元。Rothschild &amp; Co Redburn總結稱,\"鋰礦股的風險回報比不如以前那麼有吸引力\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%8B%B0%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E4%BD%8E%E8%BF%B7%E6%9C%9F%E5%B0%9A%E6%9C%AA%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F-170037365.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 01:16:16",
